Like NumberedWindows, [http://nschum.de/src/emacs/window-numbering-mode/ window-numbering.el] assigns numbers to windows for quick access (like Firefox does for tabs).  Unlike NumberedWindows, it has hooks to influence the numbering of special windows.

http://nschum.de/src/emacs/window-numbering-mode/window-numbering.png

See also: NumberedWindows

CategoryWindows


